### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### Create a laptop order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "item": "laptop",
  "amount": 2,
  "price": 999.99
}

### Create a keyboard order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "item": "keyboard",
  "amount": 5,
  "price": 49.99
}

### Create a mouse order (default amount=1, price=9.99)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "item": "mouse"
}

### --- Error cases ---

### Missing item field
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 100
}

### Invalid JSON
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

not-json

### Runtime statistics (memory, goroutines)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stats
